an]] |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/1999/apr/05/5 |accessdate=17 October 2018 |location=London |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |last=Brugui\u00e8re |first=Jean-Louis |date=17 November 2006 |title=Report |work=Paris Court of Serious Claims |url=http://www.lexpress.fr/info/monde/dossier/rwanda/PDF/rwanda.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061216011534/http://www.lexpress.fr/info/monde/dossier/rwanda/PDF/rwanda.pdf |archivedate=16 December 2006 |accessdate=17 October 2018 |ref=harv|language=fr}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Byman |first1=Daniel |last2=Chalk |first2=Peter |last3=Hoffman |first3=Bruce |last4=Rosenau |first4=William |last5=Brannan |first5=David |year=2001 |title=Trends in Outside Support for Insurgent Movements |publisher=Rand Corporation |url=https://books.google.com/?id=R0a11NarYXcC |isbn=978-0-8330-3232-4 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Carney |first=J.J. |year=2013 |title=Rwanda Before the Genocide: Catholic Politics and Ethnic Discourse in the Late Colonial Era |location=Oxford |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=978-0-19-998227-1 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=IawzAAAAQBAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |author=Central Intelligence Agency (CIA) (I) |work=[[The World Factbook]] |title=Rwanda |authorlink=CIA |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/rw.html |accessdate=17 October 2018 | ref = {{sfnRef|CIA (I)}} }}\n* {{cite book |last=Chr\u00e9tien |first=Jean-Pierre |year=2003 |title=The Great Lakes of Africa: Two Thousand Years of History |location=Cambridge, Mass. |publisher=MIT Press |isbn=978-1-890951-34-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ezo5PQAACAAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Cunningham |first=David E. |title=Barriers to Peace in Civil War |publisher=Cambridge University Press |date=2011 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nNNNCk8BfjUC&dq= |isbn=9781139499408 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Dallaire |first=Rom\u00e9o |year=2003 |title=Shake Hands with the Devil: The Failure of Humanity in Rwanda |location=London |publisher=Arrow |isbn=978-0-09-947893-5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ja2hQgAACAAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news |last=Dash |first=Leon |date=2 December 1983 |title=Many Rwandan Refugees Moving North in Uganda to Escape Attacks |work=[[Washington Post]] |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/politics/1983/12/02/many-rwandan-refugees-moving-north-in-uganda-to-escape-attacks/72af64c6-a040-42a9-b0ef-28ac18596a94/ |accessdate=17 October 2018 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=de Brouwer |first=Anne-Marie L. M. |year=2005 |title=Supranational Criminal Prosecution of Sexual Violence: The ICC and the Practice of the ICTY and the ICTR |publisher=Intersentia |isbn=978-90-5095-533-1 |location=Antwerp and Oxford |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite report |last=Des Forges |first=Alison |authorlink=Alison Des Forges |year=1999 |title=Leave None to Tell the Story: Genocide in Rwanda |url=https://www.hrw.org/legacy/reports/1999/rwanda/rwanda0399.htm |location=New York, NY |publisher=[[Human Rights Watch]] |isbn=1-56432-171-1 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Dorsey |first=Learthen |year=1994 |title=Historical Dictionary of Rwanda |location=Metuchen, N.J. |publisher=Scarecrow Press |isbn=978-0-8108-2820-9 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |last=Emizet |first=Kisangani N. F. |title=The Massacre of Refugees in Congo: A Case of UN Peacekeeping Failure and International Law |journal=[[Journal of Modern African Studies]] |date=July 2000 |volume=38 |issue=2 |pages=163\u2013202 |jstor=161648 |ref=harv|doi=10.1017/S0022278X0000330X }}\n* {{cite web |url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/Juvenal-Habyarimana |title=Juv\u00e9nal Habyarimana |encyclopedia=Encyclopaedia Britannica |accessdate=17 January 2019 |ref={{harvid|Encyclopaedia Britannica}}}}\n* {{cite book |last=Fassbender |first=Bardo |year=2011 |title=Securing Human Rights?: Achievements and Challenges of the UN Security Council |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=978-0-19-964149-9 |location=Oxford  |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=N8Tp8dWRtscC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Gourevitch |first=Philip |year=2000 |title=We Wish To Inform You That Tomorrow We Will Be Killed With Our Families |edition=Reprint |location=London; New York |publisher=Picador |isbn=978-0-330-37120-9 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8OiMfpTiApQC |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite web |author=Government of Rwanda |year=2009 |title=Chronology of Events Leading to Liberation |work=Official Website of the Government of Rwanda |url=http://www.gov.rw/liberation15/index.php?option=com_content&view=category&layout=blog&id=37&Itemid=55 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307130518/http://www.gov.rw/liberation15/index.php?option=com_content&view=category&layout=blog&id=37&Itemid=55 |archivedate=7 March 2012 |accessdate=17 October 2018 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Guichaoua |first=Andr\u00e9 |title=From War to Genocide: Criminal Politics in Rwanda, 1990\u20131994 |date=2015 |publisher=University of Wisconsin Press |isbn=9780299298203 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite news |last=Henley |first=Jon |date=31 October 2007 |title=Scar tissue |work=The Guardian |location=London |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2007/oct/31/rwanda.theatre |accessdate=17 October 2018 |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite map |author=ITMB Publishing |title=Rwanda & Burundi |publisher=ITMB Publishing |edition=4th Revised |isbn=978-1-55341-382-0 |url=https://www.amazon.co.uk/Rwanda-Burundi-International-Travel-Maps/dp/1553413822 |location=Richmond, B.C. |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Jones |first=Bruce D. |year=2001 |title=Peacemaking in Rwanda: The Dynamics of Failure |publisher=Lynne Rienner Publishers |isbn=978-1-5558-7994-5 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=F-SGQgAACAAJ |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=King |first=David C. |year=2007 |title=Rwanda (Cultures of the World) |location=New York |publisher=Benchmark Books |isbn=978-0-7614-2333-1 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1yLx1zSuh_QC |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Kinzer |