orium]]''\n| 2007\n| Mr. Edward Magorium\n| [[Zach Helm]]\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kung Fu Panda]]''\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2008\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Master Shifu\n| [[John Stevenson (director)|John Stevenson]] & [[Mark Osborne (filmmaker)|Mark Osborne]]\n| Voice\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Kung Fu Panda (2008)|url=http://www.allmovie.com/movie/kung-fu-panda-v354676|publisher=[[AllMovie]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]|accessdate=June 9, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Secrets of the Furious Five]]''\n| [[Raman Hui]]\n| Voice<br/>Short film\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Last Chance Harvey]]''\n| Harvey Shine\n| [[Joel Hopkins]]\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Tale of Despereaux (film)|The Tale of Despereaux]]''\n| Roscuro\n| [[Sam Fell]] & Robert Stevenhagen\n| Voice\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Barney's Version (film)|Barney's Version]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2010\n| Israel \"Izzy\" Panofsky\n| [[Richard J. Lewis]]\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Jews and Baseball: An American Love Story]]''\n| Narrator\n| Peter Miller\n| Voice<br/>Documentary\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Little Fockers]]''\n| Bernie Focker\n| [[Paul Weitz (filmmaker)|Paul Weitz]]\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kung Fu Panda 2]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2011\n| rowspan=\"2\"|Master Shifu\n| {{Sort|Yuh|[[Jennifer Yuh Nelson]]}}\n| Voice\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Kung Fu Panda (2011)|url=http://www.allmovie.com/movie/kung-fu-panda-2-v471909|publisher=[[AllMovie]]. [[Rovi Corporation]]|accessdate=June 9, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kung Fu Panda: Secrets of the Ma