 Wings That Work]]''\n| 1991\n| Milquetoast the Cross-Dressing Cockroach \n| Skip Jones\n| Voice<br/>Television special\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Liberty's Kids]]''\n| 2002\u20132003\n| [[Benedict Arnold]] (voice)\n| {{n/a}}\n| Voice<br/>4 episodes\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tinubu|first1=Aramide|title=27 Stars You Didn't Know Voiced Popular Cartoon Characters|url=http://www.hollywood.com/celebrities/stars-you-didnt-know-voiced-popular-cartoon-characters-60487575/#/ms-22571/19|website=[[Hollywood.com]]|accessdate=25 April 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Curb Your Enthusiasm]]''\n| 2005\n| Larry's Guide #1\n| [[Larry Charles]]\n| Episode: \"The End\"\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tharpe|first1=Frazier|title=The 25 Best \"Curb Your Enthusiasm\" Episodes|url=http://uk.complex.com/pop-culture/2013/08/best-curb-your-enthusiasm-episodes/the-end|website=[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]|accessdate=25 April 2016|date=10 August 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Kung Fu Panda Holiday]]''\n|2010\n|Master Shifu\n|[[Tim Johnson (film director)|Tim Johnson]] \n|Voice<br/>Television special\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"AllMovie\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Luck (TV series)|Luck]]''\n| 2011\u20132012\n| Chester Bernstein\n| Various\n| 9 episodes; also producer\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=HBO cancels Dustin Hoffman drama Luck after horse death|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-17364029|website=[[BBC News]]|publisher=[[BBC]]|accessdate=25 April 2016|date=15 March 2012}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Roald Dahl's Esio Trot]]''\n| 2015\n| Mr Henry Hoppy\n| [[Dearbhla Walsh]]\n| Television film\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Medici: Masters of Florence]]''\n| 2016\n| [[Giovanni di Bicci de' Medici|Giovanni de' Medici]]\n| [[Sergio Mimica-Gezzan]]\n| 5 episodes\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|last1=Petski|first1=Denis